&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Please Note: This is an Expression of Interest application for future opportunities.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;em&gt; While we don’t have an immediate, active opening attached to this specific posting, we are always looking ahead for exceptional sales talent. By applying here, you are joining our proactive talent pool for future hiring waves.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
